Read a Dataset-JSON file

Source: R/read.R
read_ds_json.Rd

read_ds_json() reads a Dataset-JSON into R.

Usage

read_ds_json(file)

Arguments

file

A path to a Dataset-JSON file.

Value

A ds_json object.

Examples

read_ds_json(ds_json_example_path("ae"))
